---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Entertainment Accounting — CA Accounting | Music, Film, TV"
  description="Specialty accounting for entertainment professionals: musicians, actors, producers, directors, and agencies. Tour accounting, royalties, residuals, loan-out corporations, and IP valuation."
>
  <section class="bg-cream-warm py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <p class="text-forest font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-6 fade-in">Industries · Entertainment</p>
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-serif text-navy leading-tight mb-6 fade-in fade-in-delay-1">
          Accounting for the people who make the work.
        </h1>
        <p class="text-charcoal text-lg leading-relaxed fade-in fade-in-delay-2">
          We handle the accounting and tax work for working musicians, actors, producers, directors, writers, technicians, and the agencies behind them. Our job is to make the financial side disappear so you can focus on the creative one.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-12 mb-16">
        <div class="lg:col-span-1 fade-in">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif text-navy mb-4">What we handle</h2>
          <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-base leading-relaxed">
            Entertainment income comes from a dozen different places — and each one comes with its own rules. We've spent twenty years learning them all.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-2 fade-in fade-in-delay-1">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy mb-2">Tour accounting</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">Settlement reviews, per diem reconciliation, multi-state and international payroll, and tour-end financial reporting alongside your tour manager and promoter.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy mb-2">Royalty tracking</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">Mechanical, performance, sync, and streaming royalty audits and reconciliation with PROs, publishers, and labels.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy mb-2">Residuals & participations</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">SAG-AFTRA, WGA, DGA residuals tracking and reconciliation, plus profit-participation accounting for producers and creators.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy mb-2">Loan-out corporations</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">S-corp loan-out structures for actors, directors, musicians, and other working creatives — set up correctly and maintained year over year.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy mb-2">IP & copyright valuation</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">Valuation of catalogs, libraries, and creative IP for sale, gifting, estate planning, or partner transactions.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy mb-2">Multi-state filings</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">Production-state filings, residency planning, and credit allocation for income earned across multiple states.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-navy text-cream py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div class="fade-in">
          <p class="text-cream/60 font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Who we work with</p>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif text-cream mb-6">
            Working creatives, all levels.
          </h2>
          <p class="text-cream/80 text-base leading-relaxed">
            From an actor with a first speaking role to a producer running a slate of projects, the financial complexity scales with the career. We work with clients across that whole range — and the tools and structures we recommend grow with you.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3 text-cream/70 text-sm fade-in fade-in-delay-1">
          <div class="border border-cream/10 rounded p-4">Musicians & songwriters</div>
          <div class="border border-cream/10 rounded p-4">Actors</div>
          <div class="border border-cream/10 rounded p-4">Producers & directors</div>
          <div class="border border-cream/10 rounded p-4">Writers</div>
          <div class="border border-cream/10 rounded p-4">Agencies & managers</div>
          <div class="border border-cream/10 rounded p-4">Technicians & crew</div>
          <div class="border border-cream/10 rounded p-4">Composers</div>
          <div class="border border-cream/10 rounded p-4">Production companies</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto fade-in">
        <p class="text-forest font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-8 text-center">In Our Clients' Words</p>
        <div class="text-forest/30 font-serif text-9xl leading-none mb-[-2rem] text-center select-none" aria-hidden="true">"</div>
        <blockquote class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-serif text-navy leading-snug mb-10 text-center">
          Farshid and all his team have been instrumental in strengthening our financial understanding.
        </blockquote>
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <div class="w-12 h-px bg-forest mx-auto mb-4"></div>
          <p class="text-charcoal font-semibold">Dave Mason</p>
          <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm">Rock and Roll Hall of Fame inductee</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 pt-12 border-t border-line">
          <div class="border-l-2 border-forest pl-6 fade-in">
            <p class="text-charcoal text-base leading-relaxed mb-4 italic">
              "We consider Farshid and the entire CA Accounting staff family now, and wouldn't know what to do without them."
            </p>
            <p class="text-charcoal font-semibold text-sm">Octavius & Jamal Terry-Sims</p>
            <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-xs">Fashion designer & choreographer / director</p>
          </div>
          <div class="border-l-2 border-forest pl-6 fade-in fade-in-delay-1">
            <p class="text-charcoal text-base leading-relaxed mb-4 italic">
              "Farshid is an absolute wizard of accounting and has saved me many a precious dollar."
            </p>
            <p class="text-charcoal font-semibold text-sm">David Norton</p>
            <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-xs">President, Ladder Up Media</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center mt-12">
          <a href="/testimonials" class="link-underline text-forest font-semibold text-sm">More client stories →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-cream-warm py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center fade-in">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif text-navy mb-6">
          Ready to clean up your accounting?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-charcoal text-base leading-relaxed mb-10">
          Schedule a free consultation. Bring last year's return, your latest royalty statement, or anything you would like us to review — we will look at it together.
        </p>
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="btn-modern inline-block bg-forest text-cream font-semibold px-10 py-4 rounded hover:bg-forest-hover transition-colors"
        >
          Schedule a Free Consultation
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
